data.text: Carroll County is a county in the New England state of New Hampshire. It is located in the central eastern portion of the state, and borders Maine as well as Strafford County to the south, Belknap County to the southwest, Grafton County to the northwest, and Coös County to the north. Its county seat is Ossipee.
